1
00:00:43,060 --> 00:00:46,780
=Auspicious Nobles=

2
00:00:47,580 --> 00:00:49,940
=Episode 8=

3
00:00:49,940 --> 00:00:52,500
(You Stole My Rice Balls
and Still Want to Woo Me?)

4
00:00:53,110 --> 00:00:54,150
Tower Master, this is bad!

5
00:00:54,430 --> 00:00:56,600
All the rice balls
in our kitchen are gone.

6
00:00:56,820 --> 00:00:57,840
Where are my rice balls?

7
00:00:59,110 --> 00:01:00,500
- Your Highness.
- Your Highness.

8
00:01:01,840 --> 00:01:02,430
Your Highness.

9
00:01:02,900 --> 00:01:04,790
My men and I have stolen back
all the rice balls

10
00:01:04,790 --> 00:01:05,640
from the shop.

11
00:01:08,510 --> 00:01:10,480
Break every single one open
and check carefully.

12
00:01:10,950 --> 00:01:13,400
See if there are any
hidden secret notes inside.

13
00:01:16,560 --> 00:01:19,000
I still have the one-for-one
receipt stubs in my hand.

14
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:20,790
This is a scam.
I'll report it to the magistrate.

15
00:01:20,840 --> 00:01:21,920
What's going on?

16
00:01:27,480 --> 00:01:28,100
Your Highness,

17
00:01:28,200 --> 00:01:29,680
all the rice balls have been checked.

18
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:31,640
There's only glutinous rice, meat floss,

19
00:01:31,950 --> 00:01:33,280
and a huge salted egg yolk inside.

20
00:01:35,070 --> 00:01:37,120
They use authentic ingredients, huh?

21
00:01:38,350 --> 00:01:39,400
In my name,

22
00:01:40,070 --> 00:01:43,310
distribute them all
to the poor citizens in the city.

23
00:01:44,410 --> 00:01:45,350
Your Highness is wise.

24
00:01:45,800 --> 00:01:47,560
This will not only mess
with Tower Master,

25
00:01:48,100 --> 00:01:49,990
but also highlight
Your Highness's benevolence.

26
00:01:50,150 --> 00:01:51,590
They were seized by the Inspectorate.

27
00:01:52,510 --> 00:01:54,950
The Crown Prince's Residence
is handing out free rice balls

28
00:01:55,510 --> 00:01:56,560
for public relief.

29
00:01:56,700 --> 00:01:57,950
I can taste your flavor in this.

30
00:01:59,000 --> 00:01:59,970
Where are the rice balls?

31
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:02,400
Zheng Yuanhe, you've gone too far!

32
00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:04,310
Also,

33
00:02:04,920 --> 00:02:06,950
buy up all the glutinous rice
in the city for me.

34
00:02:07,870 --> 00:02:10,360
I don't care what tricks
she has up her sleeve.

35
00:02:11,310 --> 00:02:14,000
I won't leave her a single chance.

36
00:02:15,450 --> 00:02:16,800
- Yes, Your Highness.
- Yes, Your Highness.

37
00:02:16,810 --> 00:02:17,840
Are you selling them or not?

38
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:18,360
Yes...

39
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:19,560
You're not avoiding
giving them out, right?

40
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:20,030
Exactly.

41
00:02:20,030 --> 00:02:20,780
Please don't worry.

42
00:02:20,810 --> 00:02:21,900
Tell your boss to come out.

43
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:23,080
We all came early for this.

44
00:02:23,430 --> 00:02:24,030
Hurry up.

45
00:02:24,030 --> 00:02:25,190
Are you selling or not?

46
00:02:25,530 --> 00:02:26,400
Screw you. Refund us.

47
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:29,000
Have the staff tell the customers
that due to special circumstances today,

48
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:29,870
it will be
buy-one-get-two-free tomorrow.

49
00:02:29,870 --> 00:02:30,520
We'll honor it.

50
00:02:30,750 --> 00:02:31,150
Alright.

51
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:32,190
Jiuzhu,

52
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:34,360
take the brothers and use
your lightness skill

53
00:02:34,510 --> 00:02:36,520
to buy up all the glutinous rice,
salted egg yolks,

54
00:02:36,520 --> 00:02:38,890
and all the ingredients
for rice balls in the whole city now.

55
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:41,360
The scheming fool's next step
will be to cut off my supply.

56
00:02:41,750 --> 00:02:42,400
It's too late.

57
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:45,400
When I left, I saw baskets
of glutinous rice

58
00:02:45,410 --> 00:02:47,790
and salted duck eggs being hauled
into the Crown Prince's Residence.

59
00:02:50,750 --> 00:02:51,520
Tower Master...

60
00:02:52,120 --> 00:02:53,180
Tower Master, hang in there.

61
00:02:53,190 --> 00:02:55,000
Where there's life, there's hope.

62
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:57,590
Using my rice balls
to build his reputation,

63
00:02:57,590 --> 00:02:58,280
cutting off my ingredients,

64
00:02:58,280 --> 00:02:59,400
and even ruining my business.

65
00:02:59,520 --> 00:03:00,360
Hurry up.

66
00:03:00,590 --> 00:03:03,470
Zheng Yuanhe,
the black-hearted Crown Prince!

67
00:03:04,590 --> 00:03:07,190
Before I could even
achieve my small goal,

68
00:03:07,390 --> 00:03:09,280
I'm going to be worried
to death by him first.

69
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:12,470
I am irreconcilably at odds with him!

70
00:03:12,470 --> 00:03:13,400
How much longer?

71
00:03:14,470 --> 00:03:15,680
Are you selling or not?

72
00:03:17,190 --> 00:03:18,000
Tower Master, look.

73
00:03:24,590 --> 00:03:25,520
We have received reports

74
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:26,520
that Noble Rice Balls

75
00:03:26,550 --> 00:03:28,250
is suspected of fraud
against the citizens.

76
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:29,580
It is to be shut down now,

77
00:03:29,590 --> 00:03:30,880
and all proceeds are confiscated.

78
00:03:31,770 --> 00:03:32,680
Fly with the two of us.

79
00:03:32,870 --> 00:03:33,520
Two people?

80
00:03:34,190 --> 00:03:34,880
Two hundred taels.

81
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:35,910
Are you robbing us?

82
00:03:36,450 --> 00:03:37,360
Are you coming or not?

83
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:40,430
Put it on credit first.
Put it on my tab.

84
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:42,750
Coming.

85
00:03:43,030 --> 00:03:43,750
Here I am.

86
00:03:44,430 --> 00:03:46,150
You two should eat fewer rice balls.

87
00:03:46,370 --> 00:03:47,560
But I came so early for this.

88
00:03:47,600 --> 00:03:49,170
What are we supposed to do about this?

89
00:03:49,630 --> 00:03:50,360
Father,

90
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:51,470
I...

91
00:03:51,700 --> 00:03:53,470
I want to file
a complaint against Yuanhe.

92
00:03:53,470 --> 00:03:54,400
He bullied me.

93
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:57,150
Please grant me justice, Father.

94
00:03:57,910 --> 00:03:59,910
You are already a grown man.

95
00:04:00,750 --> 00:04:02,560
What a disgrace to be weeping like this.

96
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:04,400
I really suffered an injustice.

97
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:05,710
A few days ago,

98
00:04:06,030 --> 00:04:07,640
I opened a small rice ball shop.

99
00:04:07,800 --> 00:04:08,520
Originally,

100
00:04:08,690 --> 00:04:10,030
it was meant to serve the public,

101
00:04:10,170 --> 00:04:12,470
and incidentally bring some income
to the imperial merchants,

102
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:14,500
all to share your burdens, Father.

103
00:04:14,510 --> 00:04:15,400
Who would have thought

104
00:04:15,420 --> 00:04:17,630
that yesterday, Yuanhe
sent people from the Inspectorate

105
00:04:17,630 --> 00:04:19,430
to come and shut down my rice ball shop?

106
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:21,430
He even confiscated all the money.

107
00:04:22,070 --> 00:04:22,630
This move...

108
00:04:23,070 --> 00:04:23,830
This move really

109
00:04:23,830 --> 00:04:26,920
disheartens everyone
who works for the imperial court,

110
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:27,920
Father...

111
00:04:29,310 --> 00:04:30,120
Crown Prince,

112
00:04:30,510 --> 00:04:31,510
is this true?

113
00:04:33,390 --> 00:04:34,000
Father,

114
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:35,600
I received a report

115
00:04:36,160 --> 00:04:37,160
that Yuanzhao's shop

116
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:38,310
made false promises,

117
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:39,430
cheated the citizens,

118
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:40,750
and caused a riot.

119
00:04:41,070 --> 00:04:42,240
As the Crown Prince,

120
00:04:42,750 --> 00:04:44,040
in order to maintain order,

121
00:04:44,050 --> 00:04:45,900
I had no choice
but to shut it down temporarily.

122
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:48,750
Yuanzhao,

123
00:04:49,390 --> 00:04:50,800
if I let the law slide

124
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:52,310
just because you are a prince,

125
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:55,680
how can the people
trust the imperial family?

126
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:56,720
Moreover,

127
00:04:57,510 --> 00:04:59,270
I told you on the day of the shutdown

128
00:04:59,420 --> 00:05:01,000
that as soon
as the public anger is appeased,

129
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:02,600
it will be returned to you immediately.

130
00:05:03,190 --> 00:05:04,560
You are in such a hurry,

131
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:08,240
I'm afraid there is
something shameful hidden there.

132
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:10,270
I think

133
00:05:10,270 --> 00:05:12,310
you are clearly
jealous of my achievements

134
00:05:12,310 --> 00:05:13,680
and that Father
praised me over and over.

135
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:14,750
You think too highly of your...

136
00:05:14,750 --> 00:05:15,190
Enough.

137
00:05:15,190 --> 00:05:15,510
I...

138
00:05:17,430 --> 00:05:18,720
This matter ends here.

139
00:05:19,480 --> 00:05:20,160
Crown Prince,

140
00:05:21,070 --> 00:05:23,270
you must act on solid evidence

141
00:05:23,280 --> 00:05:24,800
and not make excessive assumptions.

142
00:05:26,950 --> 00:05:27,560
Yuanzhao,

143
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:29,000
behave yourself too.

144
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:31,000
Stop causing trouble all the time.

145
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:36,430
I am a bit tired.

146
00:05:38,550 --> 00:05:40,190
- Farewell, Father.
- Farewell, Father.

147
00:05:41,870 --> 00:05:43,240
Scheming with a tiger

148
00:05:45,170 --> 00:05:46,870
will only get you
eaten by it in the end.

149
00:05:48,190 --> 00:05:49,830
You think Wangshi Tower is helping you?

150
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:54,000
Don't unknowingly become
an accomplice to overthrowing the state.

151
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:56,720
I don't understand what you are saying.

152
00:05:58,480 --> 00:06:01,360
I don't care if you're
really foolish or just acting.

153
00:06:02,750 --> 00:06:04,480
If Wangshi Tower dares to show its head,

154
00:06:05,510 --> 00:06:08,000
I will suppress it to the very end.

155
00:06:18,430 --> 00:06:19,920
Then, let's see you try.

156
00:06:25,190 --> 00:06:26,870
My dear, you're back.

157
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:37,480
My dear, how did
your face get so sunburned?

158
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:38,360
Don't even mention it.

159
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:41,510
The Crown Prince made me kneel
in the courtyard for two days.

160
00:06:42,170 --> 00:06:43,360
Isn't he just playing with me?

161
00:06:44,950 --> 00:06:45,800
Have a seat quickly.

162
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:48,800
Lord Pan,

163
00:06:52,060 --> 00:06:53,510
here's His Highness's verbal command.

164
00:06:54,450 --> 00:06:56,260
"Pan Yang, you
are hardworking and resilient,

165
00:06:56,270 --> 00:06:57,310
which pleases me greatly.

166
00:06:57,570 --> 00:06:58,800
Starting the day after tomorrow,

167
00:06:58,810 --> 00:07:00,900
go to the imperial hunting grounds
in the northern woods

168
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:02,390
to guard the security of the grounds."

169
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:05,270
Good...

170
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:09,000
The imperial hunting grounds?

171
00:07:10,510 --> 00:07:11,390
I understand now.

172
00:07:12,310 --> 00:07:14,750
The Crown Prince making me
kneel in the courtyard for two days

173
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:16,720
was a test for me.

174
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:20,360
Thank you, Your Highness.

175
00:07:21,190 --> 00:07:21,750
Muyan,

176
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:23,510
go quickly and get your best box

177
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:25,800
of pearl powder to apply on my face.

178
00:07:26,510 --> 00:07:27,430
The day after tomorrow,

179
00:07:28,190 --> 00:07:29,600
I want to look my best

180
00:07:30,190 --> 00:07:31,560
when I meet His Highness.

181
00:07:33,340 --> 00:07:34,380
(To Li Qingqing)

182
00:07:34,390 --> 00:07:36,190
Crown Prince the scheming fool,
what does he mean?

183
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:38,800
He asked to meet me
at Wangshi Tower tomorrow.

184
00:07:41,190 --> 00:07:43,310
He ruined my perfectly fine
rice ball business,

185
00:07:43,310 --> 00:07:45,000
and yet he has the nerve to ask me out.

186
00:07:45,600 --> 00:07:46,510
We're doomed.

187
00:07:46,510 --> 00:07:47,160
Tower Master,

188
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:49,870
the Crown Prince
must have discovered your identity.

189
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:54,120
No,

190
00:07:54,870 --> 00:07:56,240
he probably just suspects it

191
00:07:56,260 --> 00:07:57,850
and hasn't completely confirmed it yet.

192
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:59,990
Otherwise, he would have
killed me a long time ago.

193
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:03,070
But if I don't go,

194
00:08:03,070 --> 00:08:04,660
it will only make me
look more suspicious.

195
00:08:05,300 --> 00:08:07,390
Tell Jiuzhu to lie in ambush
outside Wangshi Tower.

196
00:08:07,500 --> 00:08:09,360
In case the Crown Prince
suddenly turns on me,

197
00:08:09,510 --> 00:08:10,560
he can rush in to save me.

198
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:11,070
Alright.

199
00:08:11,300 --> 00:08:13,780
(Wangshi Tower)

200
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:28,270
(My Wangshi Tower.)

201
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:30,270
(I'm finally back.)

202
00:08:33,160 --> 00:08:34,810
(My painting,
"Phoenix Soaring the Nine Heavens".)

203
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:37,390
(I fled in such a rush that day,)

204
00:08:37,750 --> 00:08:38,600
(I forgot to take it.)

205
00:08:44,550 --> 00:08:46,440
The Master of Wangshi Tower
has immense power,

206
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:48,280
yet the artwork she creates

207
00:08:49,120 --> 00:08:50,750
is worse than a three-year-old child's.

208
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:56,870
This chicken

209
00:08:57,440 --> 00:08:58,870
is drawn so crookedly,

210
00:09:00,360 --> 00:09:02,200
and the coloring is an absolute mess.

211
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:04,000
(You're the chicken.)

212
00:09:04,270 --> 00:09:06,080
(You blind fool with no artistic sense.)

213
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:07,590
(It's abstract art, don't you get it?)

214
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:09,600
Is it possible...

215
00:09:11,840 --> 00:09:14,080
I mean, is there any possibility

216
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:15,600
that it's a phoenix

217
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:17,550
and not a chicken?

218
00:09:21,910 --> 00:09:23,390
(A soaring phoenix...)

219
00:09:24,390 --> 00:09:26,790
(That woman really wants
to overthrow Great Yong)

220
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:28,510
(and become the Empress herself.)

221
00:09:29,360 --> 00:09:30,080
To me,

222
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:32,790
it looks more like a plucked pheasant.

223
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:35,630
Let's go.

224
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:37,400
We'll take a look elsewhere.

225
00:09:39,910 --> 00:09:41,270
(Just you wait, you scheming fool.)

226
00:09:41,270 --> 00:09:42,990
(Sooner or later,
I will destroy your peace.)

227
00:10:00,750 --> 00:10:02,000
You must be tired, Miss Qingqing.

228
00:10:02,400 --> 00:10:03,690
I've prepared some tea and snacks.

229
00:10:06,360 --> 00:10:08,600
(This is a 1-to-1
replica of a modern toilet)

230
00:10:08,600 --> 00:10:09,750
(that I installed.)

231
00:10:14,060 --> 00:10:16,380
(This scheming fool is using
the toilet bowl as a tea table?)

232
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:20,790
(He's really something else.)

233
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:26,360
I find this room to be

234
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:27,320
unique,

235
00:10:27,510 --> 00:10:28,360
elegant,

236
00:10:28,720 --> 00:10:29,600
and interesting.

237
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:39,870
Listen.

238
00:10:41,550 --> 00:10:43,480
There's the sound of trickling water,

239
00:10:44,080 --> 00:10:46,110
which brings to mind
mountains and flowing rivers.

240
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:47,750
So I cleaned it up

241
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:49,200
and turned it into a tearoom.

242
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:52,390
Elegant.

243
00:10:52,960 --> 00:10:55,240
Truly elegant.

244
00:10:59,360 --> 00:11:00,150
But

245
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:02,270
the box on the wall is a bit strange.

246
00:11:03,150 --> 00:11:04,350
It has an opening at the top,

247
00:11:04,420 --> 00:11:06,000
with a piece of silk fabric halfway out.

248
00:11:06,550 --> 00:11:07,320
What is it for?

249
00:11:07,480 --> 00:11:08,670
That's a tissue box.

250
00:11:08,670 --> 00:11:09,590
It's used to wipe your a...

251
00:11:10,910 --> 00:11:12,120
(I almost slipped up.)

252
00:11:12,120 --> 00:11:12,870
Wipe what?

253
00:11:16,550 --> 00:11:17,440
To wipe...

254
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:21,440
Wipe your mouth.

255
00:11:23,320 --> 00:11:24,240
It's like,

256
00:11:24,360 --> 00:11:26,630
after you have tea and snacks like this,

257
00:11:27,120 --> 00:11:28,120
it's used to...

258
00:11:34,380 --> 00:11:35,550
It's used to wipe your mouth.

259
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:40,750
I've seen
foreign merchants use it this way.

260
00:11:42,550 --> 00:11:43,550
Miss Qingqing,

261
00:11:44,360 --> 00:11:45,910
you are very knowledgeable.

262
00:11:47,110 --> 00:11:47,890
Please have a seat.

263
00:11:48,000 --> 00:11:48,600
No.

264
00:11:52,480 --> 00:11:55,270
I'd like to see
the crossbow workshop first.

265
00:11:56,150 --> 00:11:59,030
(I don't have a habit
of drinking tea by the toilet.)

266
00:11:59,030 --> 00:11:59,480
Alright.

267
00:12:00,240 --> 00:12:00,870
It's upstairs.

268
00:12:10,410 --> 00:12:13,800
♪Snowflakes settle gently
upon your brows♪

269
00:12:14,560 --> 00:12:17,940
♪Your dark hair
brushes across my fingertips♪

270
00:12:18,710 --> 00:12:20,450
♪Your smile♪

271
00:12:20,710 --> 00:12:23,000
♪Melts away the winter snow♪

272
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:26,680
♪One fleeting glance says more
than a thousand words♪

273
00:12:27,140 --> 00:12:30,450
♪Yet I stand before you♪

274
00:12:31,190 --> 00:12:35,020
♪Unable to recognize your eyes♪

275
00:12:35,440 --> 00:12:37,360
♪Though fate tries♪

276
00:12:37,360 --> 00:12:39,940
♪To make us pass each other by♪

277
00:12:40,160 --> 00:12:43,580
♪I choose to make our story whole♪

278
00:12:43,840 --> 00:12:45,470
♪Though time slips by♪

279
00:12:45,470 --> 00:12:47,230
♪As day turns into night♪

280
00:12:47,750 --> 00:12:51,770
♪I still remember
our days at Wangshi Tower♪

281
00:12:52,190 --> 00:12:54,570
♪One glance at you lasts a lifetime♪

282
00:12:54,570 --> 00:12:56,360
♪Blessed by fate♪

283
00:12:56,360 --> 00:13:01,520
♪I believe this moment
will last forever♪

284
00:13:01,520 --> 00:13:03,960
♪Your smiling face♪

285
00:13:03,960 --> 00:13:06,800
♪Is the most beautiful poem♪

286
00:13:06,800 --> 00:13:10,420
♪I'd rather spend my days with you♪

287
00:13:10,940 --> 00:13:14,400
♪And wander the world together♪

288
00:13:14,400 --> 00:13:15,740
♪Holding you close♪

289
00:13:15,740 --> 00:13:18,280
♪Envying neither lovers nor immortals♪

290
00:13:18,280 --> 00:13:20,600
♪Your tenderness♪

291
00:13:20,600 --> 00:13:23,460
♪Is the brightest moon♪

292
00:13:23,460 --> 00:13:27,160
♪I'd rather
pledge three lifetimes to you♪

293
00:13:27,680 --> 00:13:30,970
♪Our love will never fade away♪

294
00:13:30,970 --> 00:13:33,430
♪Though heaven and earth grow old♪

295
00:13:33,960 --> 00:13:38,210
♪My heart will remain forever pure♪

